<i>adverb</i>: 허술히 [허술히], 허름히 [허름히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>허술히 [허술히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shabbily; humbly</dd><br>
<dd>낡고 헐어서 보잘것없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being old and worn out, making it look worthless.</dd><br>
<dd>2. loosely; laxly; poorly</dd><br>
<dd>꼼꼼하지 못하고 빈틈이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of showing a loophole without being meticulous.</dd><br>
<dd>3. indifferently; inattentively; negligently</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 행동이 무심하고 소홀하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of looking or acting indifferent or paying little attention to something.</dd><br>
<dt>허름히 [허름히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shabbily; raggedly; seedily</dd><br>
<dd>좀 낡은 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being rather old and worn-out.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cheaply; shabbily</dd><br>
<dd>값이 좀 싼 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being rather cheap in price.</dd><br>
<dd>3. shabbily; lowly</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 물건이 표준에 약간 미치지 못한 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of a person or an article being below a certain standard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>